## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all aspects of social media's impact on user experience. The rapidly evolving nature of social media platforms means that new trends and features could alter user experiences in unforeseen ways. Additionally, individual experiences with social media can vary widely based on personal circumstances and usage patterns, which may not be fully captured in the sources reviewed.